      "text": [
        "2324 - وَ فِي رِوَايَةٍ أُخْرَى : «أَنَّهُ كَانَ لِبَنِي هَاشِمٍ مِنَ اَلْحَجَرِ اَلْأَسْوَدِ إِلَى اَلرُّكْنِ اَلشَّامِيِّ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2324 - In another narration:\n\"The portion of the Kaaba allocated to Banu Hashim extended from the Black Stone to the Syrian Corner.\""
        ]
      }
    }
